OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with outbreaks of rain. Rain
OL,7,Fclearing to the east overnight with a
OL,8,Ffew showers lingering and some clearer
OL,9,Fspells developing. Winds strong this
OL,10,Fevening then easing overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA mixed day with some bright
OL,13,Fand sunny spells but also blustery
OL,14,Fshowers feeding in from the west.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,17,Fand strong winds spreading north on
OL,18,FSaturday with a risk of gales.
OL,19,FBlustery showers with winds easing on
OL,20,FSunday. Mostly dry with sunny spells
OL,21,Fon Monday, strong winds later.
